{"tid":57311,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老味 我真係好撚專敬啲裝修佬","createTime":"2016-12-28T01:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T16:23:25.000Z","uid":5584,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f148a0fd9f51823731ece21a357637ec2e1a7c00","tid":57311,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T01:45:50.000Z","msg":"今日係紅假期後既第一個工作天，現在係早上時間九點三十分。點解啲裝修佬竟然完全唔會偷懶，唔會射波，九點半鐘真係早餐都未食，就係度鑽鑽鑽，揼揼揼？<br />\n<br />\n對於仍然放假，臨天光先瞓既我，即刻來了一點反思，如同暮鼓晨鐘，提醒我地做人唔可以咁撚懶惰！令我不禁要大叫一聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味，我求下你俾我瞓陣喇"},{"pid":"a49fab0e7ff9917273829fd17bf11a1d4842d8a7","tid":57311,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T01:48:29.000Z","msg":"尊"},{"pid":"f36034fab810d5cfe21db1641cfb4b081b6add34","tid":57311,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:14:21.000Z","msg":"訓啦柒頭"},{"pid":"65923aa131c5918da6fef652c883e17763806b5e","tid":57311,"uid":58512,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:16:15.000Z","msg":"你唔撚好裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b8692d42608afd206917cbe1335ff7b77154c9","tid":57311,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:17:03.000Z","msg":"唔洗做呀"},{"pid":"7e1487eacec4bc1e85f90134e44dfdc2eca0aa3b","tid":57311,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:17:10.000Z","msg":"人在歐洲 屋在裝修"},{"pid":"ca1a98fa85295839fbef7ce17e17adb23ebe7f96","tid":57311,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"為左份糧 我都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1262493d749afd17f0065687d4794928f8d59025","tid":57311,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUG3Q2V95h1ZgDuPG76MZT5XwiPHai8mpE6eNsQ18YQgZ?filename=19924H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19924H.jpg&h=8e50fcff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc368d9252429fdf685ff8d2937da2d56efc2663","tid":57311,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尋日係咪勞工假？尋日見已經有裝修佬做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過冇鑽冇揼"},{"pid":"c4a8746d9ff4f4b10a42b28c58ce514eb95279c1","tid":57311,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人在歐洲 屋在裝修</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1471eff795410295ebbfbe487238380731a759ea","tid":57311,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:01:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尋日係咪勞工假？尋日見已經有裝修佬做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過冇鑽冇揼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我估裝修佬只要趕住交貨，應該好多都會拍心口照開工<br />\n<br />\n不過佢地都受噪音管制條例監管，假日唔可以發出噪音<br />\n但今日唔係紅日<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1386b76d1fc81c9e67df242db6e9577a38a494","tid":57311,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:04:04.000Z","msg":"人地判黎做，梗係趕啦，做多日就蝕人工，老西都趕"},{"pid":"c8f4edb74189382702598d6aa9b05a8a6dd75b79","tid":57311,"uid":40422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:56:31.000Z","msg":"今日唔係紅日喎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22c2a0ece00f38aecd88e2a395332257116acee","tid":57311,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"聽講佢地趕起上黎星期日都返，草草埋埋新年放足1個月"},{"pid":"1cdd175043fff4a727c4b8aa5aaf98bfbec8204f","tid":57311,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:11:36.000Z","msg":"唔洗搵食啊廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申樓上鑽咗成個月"},{"pid":"e5f0b55d5a6793b4c64bbc3c28d255e9f4ef4656","tid":57311,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:14:29.000Z","msg":"屌你放假人地撚有假放<br />\n準備開工有乜撚野問題"},{"pid":"9f827a2930f20e1670a01625a3a282df8cd2772d","tid":57311,"uid":5372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:15:30.000Z","msg":"就新年啦d人趕住交屋呀<br />\n我樓下 25號聖誕節果日..下午兩點幾都鑽野<br />\n之後屌佢老味打去管理費叫佢搞搞佢<br />\n跟手就靜左..不過仆佢個街臨到6點之前又鑽左十分鍾<br />\n然後冇哂聲氣應該收左工"},{"pid":"cc14c5e4f1b141c7919cdfc09b6cab47ecaf9d3e","tid":57311,"uid":11026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"930-1700<br />\n剩係放紅日<br />\n紅日有時都要開工<br />\n可能偷雞做下啲唔嘈既"},{"pid":"920459a9bf634776ba97324a43759968ca5f082d","tid":57311,"uid":8199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:30:34.000Z","msg":"i know that feel<br />\n份工要輪shift <br />\n有時早上返到去訓<br />\n佢又鑽鑽鑽 真係好撚慘<br />\n不過人地係果個時間入面做係合法<br />\n忍耐下啦 好快完架喇"},{"pid":"088f3f0126a7ab9ffe93308d17e4a8d3b8f1dcb9","tid":57311,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:44:25.000Z","msg":"之前我番通宵更 樓上裝修 果排真係想死"},{"pid":"07c4f2bbc4748a28ac347aa70eaf1f1993218be7","tid":57311,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"我望一望月歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主今日唔返工？<br />\n放假又留係屋企？"},{"pid":"741caa8dbeeea51caac7072eaf5cf257742639e8","tid":57311,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"係咪應該屌幫襯裝修佬嘅party?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔撚裝修佢咪無工開, 咪唔洗嘈到人"},{"pid":"2eeea78fa561633cb0b0792e1b520bcf23a664ae","tid":57311,"uid":6281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:32:50.000Z","msg":"懷疑樓主係鄰居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f70708b1b78f7166d55bb0479ca36cae033a07","tid":57311,"uid":2510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:38:03.000Z","msg":"尊"},{"pid":"ace0f1c1de2c246e001ad79078b21f1457afe97c","tid":57311,"uid":62754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日係紅假期後既第一個工作天，現在係早上時間九點三十分。點解啲裝修佬竟然完全唔會偷懶，唔會射波，九點半鐘真係早餐都未食，就係度鑽鑽鑽，揼揼揼？<br />\n<br />\n對於仍然放假，臨天光先瞓既我，即刻來了一點反思，如同暮鼓晨鐘，提醒我地做人唔可以咁撚懶惰！令我不禁要大叫一聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味，我求下你俾我瞓陣喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係咪同我住同一度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又係九點半比佢地嘈醒"}]}